  "detailed_description": "<h1>Early Access Roadmap</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2649800/extras/e4d76922bfeeec5061fa8b868656b075.avif?t=1747879978\" width=600 height=800 /></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2649800/extras/cf9b174026d571eb3d42ee685f9eded0.avif?t=1747879978\" width=636 height=358 /></span><br><br><strong>Vine Card is a deck-building strategic game with roguelike elements. <br>Choose from a roster of quirky heroes with even quirkier skills, <br>plan your route around the game board, <br>grab the goodies and defeat the baddies!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2649800/extras/a40c1fec3e719a339236e78d38090c9f.avif?t=1747879978\" width=636 height=127 /></span><br>Navigate your hero around a game board of limited grids, one step at a time. <br>Sounds boring? Well, throw in a deck of 200+ unique cards, and watch the chemical reactions happen. <br>8 playable characters with wildly different styles/skills further increase the fun.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2649800/extras/ae875bb7c221ae7a2fbc0ebb0f529291.poster.avif?t=1747879978\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2649800/extras/ae875bb7c221ae7a2fbc0ebb0f529291.webm?t=1747879978\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2649800/extras/ae875bb7c221ae7a2fbc0ebb0f529291.mp4?t=1747879978\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2649800/extras/3092ae20129556c95262a0326c6a08bd.avif?t=1747879978\" width=636 height=127 /></span><br>It all starts from this fictitious empire on a fictitious planet. The Tang Empire is facing a pivotal moment and from there, things start to go wild. <br>Follow our heroes from the Tang Empire to the Far West, then the mysterious Skyland descending from the, duh, sky! <br>Embark on a journey that is natural, semi-natural, supernatural, meta-natural, and unnatural at the same time! <br>Blend Wuxia and science fiction and fantasy and mythology together and it just works.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2649800/extras/09f6599b570dd0cd627b3334dd603d34.poster.avif?t=1747879978\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2649800/extras/09f6599b570dd0cd627b3334dd603d34.webm?t=1747879978\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2649800/extras/09f6599b570dd0cd627b3334dd603d34.mp4?t=1747879978\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2649800/extras/9ba4cd3291e021e2ce2eebd774c0e92f.avif?t=1747879978\" width=636 height=127 /></span><br>Take elements from Chinese mythology, Norse mythology, Celtic mythology, Arthurian mythology, Cthulhu mythology (yeah, we've got that covered, too), add modern pop culture, sprinkle a liberal dose of actual history, serve while hot.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2649800/extras/e5c2301fe4f9b9960639c4ea717fcaf4.poster.avif?t=1747879978\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2649800/extras/e5c2301fe4f9b9960639c4ea717fcaf4.webm?t=1747879978\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2649800/extras/e5c2301fe4f9b9960639c4ea717fcaf4.mp4?t=1747879978\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2649800/extras/d49da0f87084ee7bec3848aac28d019f.avif?t=1747879978\" width=636 height=127 /></span><br>Gatling guns vs swords vs crossbows vs pretty much anything you can think of. <br>Who said cowboys can't do Chinese kungfu, eh? Leave common sense behind, dude. It's holding you down.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2649800/extras/f2ee6932f73bb5a4827b430c19dfc8f7.poster.avif?t=1747879978\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2649800/extras/f2ee6932f73bb5a4827b430c19dfc8f7.webm?t=1747879978\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2649800/extras/f2ee6932f73bb5a4827b430c19dfc8f7.mp4?t=1747879978\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2649800/extras/bd7fd182695200b3d762c14ae4731e73.avif?t=1747879978\" width=636 height=127 /></span><br>The game comes with 30+ handcrafted \"legend site\" stages, from the mysterious Sanxingdui to the isle of Avalon to the glorious Valhalla. <br>Take a break from the busy combat and solve these special challenges instead!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2649800/extras/0c2afa6183aa6086d8c00db48d739faa.poster.avif?t=1747879978\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2649800/extras/0c2afa6183aa6086d8c00db48d739faa.webm?t=1747879978\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2649800/extras/0c2afa6183aa6086d8c00db48d739faa.mp4?t=1747879978\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2649800/extras/cf9b174026d571eb3d42ee685f9eded0.avif?t=1747879978\" width=636 height=358 /></span><br><br><strong>Vine Card is a deck-building strategic game with roguelike elements. <br>Choose from a roster of quirky heroes with even quirkier skills, <br>plan your route around the game board, <br>grab the goodies and defeat the baddies!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2649800/extras/a40c1fec3e719a339236e78d38090c9f.avif?t=1747879978\" width=636 height=127 /></span><br>Navigate your hero around a game board of limited grids, one step at a time. <br>Sounds boring? Well, throw in a deck of 200+ unique cards, and watch the chemical reactions happen. <br>8 playable characters with wildly different styles/skills further increase the fun.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2649800/extras/ae875bb7c221ae7a2fbc0ebb0f529291.poster.avif?t=1747879978\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2649800/extras/ae875bb7c221ae7a2fbc0ebb0f529291.webm?t=1747879978\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2649800/extras/ae875bb7c221ae7a2fbc0ebb0f529291.mp4?t=1747879978\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2649800/extras/3092ae20129556c95262a0326c6a08bd.avif?t=1747879978\" width=636 height=127 /></span><br>It all starts from this fictitious empire on a fictitious planet. The Tang Empire is facing a pivotal moment and from there, things start to go wild. <br>